channel.title: L33tpwnzscape v2 release (317)
channel.description:
[center][size=36pt]L33tpwnzscape V2 Release!!!!![/size][/center]
**forgot to add links. going to upload and put links in in a few minutes. I know I said I was going to release it a looooooooooooooooooooong time ago, but i ran into some things (school) and I didn't get the time to work on the server. I finally found some time to work on it and I began doing a ton of work. I've added a great deal of things. Hope you guys enjoy :D
V1 post link: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,452564.msg3316062.html#msg3316062]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,452564.msg3316062.html#msg3316062[/url]
[center][size=24pt]Server Features[/size][/center] [size=18pt] -all skills work! -Working dfs -veng works in pvp combat -All barrows specials -New whip gfx -All godsword specials work 100%!!! -d claws -Spirit shields -Dagon'hai robes -Elite Black armor -Edible easter egg and pumpkin! -P ring and necklace with epic high stats! -Skillcapes and skill hoods -sara brews and super restores (3:1 brew to restore ratio as in regular Runescape) -working slayer assignments -working slayer gem -Godwars -7 wave fight caves -corp beast -kalphite queen -Mithril dragon -dagannoth kings -troll training area -experiment training area -barrows -assualt -fight pits- get barrows gloves as a reward -pest control -pvp point system with an exchange shop -duel arena -king black dragon -chaos elemental -new hitpoint bar -random event (click on a skill in an onscreen menu) -::lock and ::unlock (to lock/unlock your experience gaining) These are all the ones I can think of off the top of my head, but there are tons more.[/size]
Time for pictures :P
